MetaData.title: The Weeknd - Drive (Official Music Video)
MetaData.description:

Official music video for “Drive” available everywhere now: http://theweeknd.co/HurryUpTomorrow

Directed by Trey Shults

comments.comment: I will always feel high on life when listening to the weekend

comments.comment: Ahhh yes Drive. The cure and cause of my depression visualised.
comments.author: @judahtheodor

comments.comment: Listening to this song after healing, then finding the love of your life brings uncontrollable tears of joy. Well done Abel
comments.author: @peatrisb

comments.comment: The song drives me somewhere so far 💔
comments.author: @JERRY_HEIL

comments.comment: This song+driving late at night with your windows down= heavenly experience
comments.author: @AdoobyShorts

comments.comment: Drive hands down the most underrated song off the album
comments.author: @whenevandoesthis5412

comments.comment: 3:07 I like how they made the music louder when she turned up the volume; thought that was cool.
comments.author: @lilsmoochesxoxo

comments.comment: The Weeknd is not just an artist, he's an entity.
comments.author: @Bongani-j2q

comments.comment:
Please don't end your era.
Make more songs in future.
Keep uploading.
comments.author: @Freedom83125

comments.comment: Baptized in fear You need to have a music video 😢😢😢
comments.author: @Ischaves_xo

comments.comment: The tears that whelemed up in my eyes as I watched this. No one will ever the know the nostalgia  of driving through an evening or night breeze with a sunset or just city lights. Abel really is one of the only artists that creates great music in this era
comments.author: @ElaPrimeT

comments.comment: The vibe, the vocals, the lyrics… perfection❤
comments.author: @ibrohimme

comments.comment: 4:30 Thanks for the jumpscare while I'm listening to your melodious voice Abel😑❤
comments.author: @anurag9240

comments.comment: after listening to this song i went into gta 5 and drove through all the places in the video :face-fuchsia-tongue-out::face-fuchsia-tongue-out::face-fuchsia-tongue-out:

comments.comment: 4:03 this man has the coolest pop voice in the industry
